	   <tr><td colspan=2>Another good way of getting from 20 to 25 is to kite Cordelia Minster at the Spires in North Karanas near the stone bridge- She is on a nine minute spawn which is just about long enough to regain the mana that you used killing her. The West Karanas zone isn't too far away if you look like losing (don't try the Bridge zone- the guards MAY attack you while attacking her). You can also pick up the odd griffawn in between if mana levels permit. You will get bad faction hits with bards, but I killed her hundreds of times before Cordelia conned as apprehensive- time to move on to something different when this happens.<br>Experience is excellent and loot can be from a few silver to 2 plat with the odd words, runes, etc.<br>Just keep Sow up and an eye on where Guard Frederick is (he will stick up for her if you get too close to him).<br><br>Good hunting friends!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
