	   <tr><td colspan=2>It's been my experience to selectively buff.&nbsp;&nbsp;I will give SoW to everybody, and Skin to everybody.  I will give strength to the tanks and give them damage shield as well.  I normally will not give buffs like strength to the casters because they normally won't be meleeing. I will however give it to them if they specifically ask for it. <br>I immediately snare the target so if it does go after my casters, I have time to target the caster, cast damage shield, and keep them healed until the tanks can pull off the mob.  I also cast on myself first to act as the timer.<br>&nbsp;<br>Milquetoast Outland<br>Druid of Tunare-Karana</td></tr>
