	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you are using the pure kiting method of snare / burn...&nbsp;&nbsp;I don't reccomend using a DoT at all.  They are not mana efficient when your mob is simply snared.<br><br>With the fear animal method, I can see how the mob would be moving slow enough for your DoT to reach it's full effect, but not with the simple snare.<br><br>You are better off to fire out 2 more careless lightning with the mana that to waste it on a possible resist and definate weakened DoT.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Quimby Thistlebritches<br>Druid of Karana<br><br>Sacred Order of Shadows</td></tr>
