	   <tr><td colspan=2>The ancient croc in Upper Guk is a good place to fight when you are 31; just remember that you need to root and either blast or DoT them to death - no room to kite. Another good possibility is to go to Highkeep and get into a Warrior / Raider room group. I have heard that a character can stay in there till around 35 or so. One final suggestion would be to find a group outside of Splitpaw in South Karana. The Tesch Mas Gnolls are good experience as well for the younger classes, till 35 or so..maybe a bit higher. Hope this helps you out a bit... <br><br>Aric Granath <br>- Yakage Tris'Adelfos, 51st druid, Tarew Marr<br><br>P.S.&nbsp;&nbsp;Sorry to doublepost, but I was unaware that I had to log in before posting.  My apologies... =)<br>&nbsp;<br>Aric Granath<br> - Yakage Tris'Adelfos, Druid, Tarew Marr</td></tr>
