	   <tr><td colspan=2>One tactic I evolved with Hill Giants in Rathe Mountains was to snare a giant a fair distance from our pull spot, then blast as I bring him back.&nbsp;&nbsp;I budget myself about the same amount of mana I would use blasting with the group and try to be about 2/3 into that amount by the time I get to my groupmates.  By the time my compatriots start shooting, I'm so far up the hate list on the giant that all I have to do is run him back and forth in front of my friends, who can do their killing without having him turn on them.  Do a maintenance blast every once in a while to ensure your exalted position on that list if necessary.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
