	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Aug 23rd 3:05 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Snare lasts two minutes every time (actually it seems to last a little longer as you get higher level, but you can count on 2 minutes).<br><br>To kite safely here, don't use root (as that breaks snare), just snare and nuke, timing your snare spell, and resnare at 1 min 30 sec (to allow for a few resist).<br><br>Shouldn't have any problems at all unless something else spots you while you're kiting (in which case you can either root or snare it too).<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
	   </form></table><ul>
